TestTagWritesPairsOntoCurrentCall
/ The `tag` action with key=value pairs writes both into %!callStack.Current.Tags%. Tags is lazy-allocated so the writer always succeeds regardless of the tags flag.
- tag critical=true, owner=checkout
- assert %!callStack.Current.Tags.critical% equals "true"
- assert %!callStack.Current.Tags.owner% equals "checkout"
